-Supports 64 players.
-Thanks goes to H2 for custom textures.
-Dedicated to AceServ community. Visit www.aceserv.net for more info.

    CHANGELOG
Made Church Windows breakable + altered ceiling beams to be more balanced.
Made ChimneyHouse's window smaller, altered props and light.
Fixed players climbing walls in cave.
Props, lights and other changes made to caves.
Added helpful decals for teleporters and the like.
Helped to prevent players teleporting inside eachother by pushing players after they teleport.
Minor architecture + atmosphere changes almost everywhere.

Enjoy.
